description: Cornerstone Financial Corporation operates as the bank holding company for Cornerstone Bank that provides various banking products and services for individuals and businesses. The company accepts checking and money market, savings, certificates of deposit, and individual retirement accounts. Its loan products include home equity line of credit; term and small business administration/government backed loans; business line of credit and letters of credit; and commercial mortgages. The company also offers remote deposit capture, reorder check, and online banking services. Cornerstone Financial Corporation was founded in 1999 and is based in Mount Laurel, New Jersey.
